headline: Intuit and Cherry Bekaert Partner to Accelerate Mid-Market Business Growth with AI-native Technology and Advisory Services
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. & RALEIGH, N.C., November 13, 2025--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, today announced a partnership with Cherry Bekaert, a top 20 advisory, assurance, and tax firm, to deliver Intuit Enterprise Suite to the firm’s growing client list of businesses needing a powerful, AI-native, ERP solution that drives growth.
